@import './styles/config.styl'

.navbar
  padding 0.7rem 1.5rem
  line-height $navbarHeight - 1.4rem
  position relative
  a, span, img
    display inline-block
  .logo
    height $navbarHeight - 1.4rem
    min-width $navbarHeight - 1.4rem
    margin-right 0.8rem
    vertical-align top
  .site-name
    font-size 1.3rem
    font-weight 600
    color $textColor
    position relative
  .links
    font-size 0.9rem
    position absolute
    right 1.5rem
    top 0.7rem

@media (max-width: $MQMobile)
  .navbar
    padding-left 4rem
    .can-hide
      display none
